trans-unit.source: When applied to a service operation, indicates the ASP.NET output cache profile in the configuration file that should be used by WCF to cache responses from the operation in the ASP .NET Output Cache.
trans-unit.target: 套用到服務作業時，表示組態檔中的 ASP.NET 輸出快取設定檔，WCF 應該使用此設定檔快取 ASP .NET 輸出快取中的作業傳來的回應。

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[crabout](~/includes/crabout-md.md)] the kinds of setting you can make with the Output Cache Profile, see [ASP.NET Cache Settings](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=179061).
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[crabout](~/includes/crabout-md.md)] 類型的設定，您可以進行輸出快取設定檔，請參閱[ASP.NET 快取設定](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=179061)。

trans-unit.source: The following example shows how to apply the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Web.AspNetCacheProfileAttribute> attribute to a service operation.
trans-unit.target: 下列範例會示範如何將 <xref:System.ServiceModel.Web.AspNetCacheProfileAttribute> 屬性套用到服務作業。

trans-unit.source: In this case, the cache profile named "CacheFor60Seconds" will be used for the `GetCustomer` operation
trans-unit.target: 在此情況下，名為"CacheFor60Seconds"快取設定檔將用於`GetCustomer`作業

trans-unit.source: The following configuration snippet shows how the "CacheFor60Seconds" cache profile is specified.
trans-unit.target: 下列組態片段示範如何指定"CacheFor60Seconds"快取設定檔。
